Actually, I've always dreamed of performing in front of lots of people and wanted to move to Tokyo...

131
00:16:04,004 --> 00:16:08,504
ちょっと勇気が出なくて...
But I just couldn't build up the courage...

132
00:16:08,504 --> 00:16:10,504
うわ、え？
Whoa, eh?

133
00:16:10,504 --> 00:16:14,504
「はじめなら大丈夫」？「いける」？
"Hajime will be fine"? "You can do it"?

134
00:16:14,504 --> 00:16:18,304
