"Cute", "What?" Ah, "Great dancing!" Wow, I'm getting praised!

136
00:16:22,504 --> 00:16:26,804
あ、かっこいい！褒められてる！
Ah, "Cool!" I'm being praised!

137
00:16:26,804 --> 00:16:31,504
