Alright! Since everyone gave me so much courage, Hajime...

138
00:16:31,504 --> 00:16:36,004
行ってきます！夢を目指して、上京してくる！
Is off! I'm moving to Tokyo to pursue my dream!

139
00:16:36,004 --> 00:16:39,504
